As a user, I want to log on and get playing.

As a user, I want to play the computer if I don't have anyone nearby.

As a user, I want to log on fast and play a game while waiting in line.

As a user, I want to log on and keep playing into the night without reloading the page.

As a user, I want to be able to change my password.

As a user, I want a choice to play with a friend or the computer.
